Regional Office (RO) is developing and promoting conceptual frameworks and practical guidance notes around cognitive capital  multidimensional child poverty  resilience oriented social protection  public finance for children and child friendly urbanization to provide strategic direction and operational guidance to the programming of UNICEF sectors and country offices in the region.
